00:12:39,516 --> 00:12:40,649
-Huh?

258
00:12:40,683 --> 00:12:41,149
-Huh?

259
00:12:43,516 --> 00:12:45,316
-That's why we should
be taking precautions.

260
00:12:50,183 --> 00:12:52,149
-Kiyomi Takada.

261
00:12:52,183 --> 00:12:53,216
What an idiot.

262
00:12:53,249 --> 00:12:55,283
She doesn't even realize
that Light's just

263
00:12:55,316 --> 00:12:56,949
using her for his investigation.

264
00:12:56,983 --> 00:12:58,183
-Don't say that.

265
00:12:58,216 --> 00:12:59,816
You might end up dead
if she hears you.

266
00:12:59,849 --> 00:13:01,249
-Duh, I know that.

267
00:13:01,283 --> 00:13:04,616
That's why I
whispered it quietly.

268
00:13:04,649 --> 00:13:06,083
Hey!

269
00:13:06,116 --> 00:13:08,516
She snickered at me!

270
00:13:08,549 --> 00:13:10,949
