271
00:13:10,983 --> 00:13:11,616
-Hang on!

272
00:13:16,616 --> 00:13:19,183
-What were you trying to do?

273
00:13:19,216 --> 00:13:20,716
-What was I doing?

274
00:13:20,749 --> 00:13:21,683
What about you?

275
00:13:24,683 --> 00:13:26,516
Grr.

276
00:13:26,549 --> 00:13:28,916
-Lidner, that young
lady is actually

277
00:13:28,949 --> 00:13:30,649
