278
00:13:30,683 --> 00:13:33,416
Please, you shouldn't
be so rough with her.

279
00:13:33,449 --> 00:13:34,216
-Hmph!

280
00:13:34,249 --> 00:13:35,983
-Of course, Miss Takada.

281
00:13:36,016 --> 00:13:37,316
Please, excuse me.

282
00:13:40,116 --> 00:13:43,449
-Misa Misa, are you all right?

283
00:13:43,483 --> 00:13:47,216
-That was so frustrating!

284
00:13:47,249 --> 00:13:49,083
