him for a moment?

288
00:13:55,649 --> 00:13:57,049
-Near, this is Aizawa.

289
00:13:57,083 --> 00:13:58,349
What is it?

290
00:13:58,383 --> 00:14:00,149
NEAR: I have a question
regarding surveillance for L

