00:14:00,183 --> 00:14:01,616
and Takada's meetings.

292
00:14:01,649 --> 00:14:03,716
Are you recording both
audio and video feed

293
00:14:03,749 --> 00:14:05,049
to their conversations?

294
00:14:05,083 --> 00:14:05,983
-Uh, no.

295
00:14:06,016 --> 00:14:07,983
Only an audio feed right now.

296
00:14:08,016 --> 00:14:09,183
NEAR: I see.

297
00:14:09,216 --> 00:14:10,916
Only wiretaps at the moment.

298
00:14:10,949 --> 00:14:12,183
How interesting.

299
00:14:12,216 --> 00:14:14,816
Thank you very much.

300
00:14:14,849 --> 00:14:17,049
-If they're only using
wiretaps, then it's

301
00:14:17,083 --> 00:14:20,016
