serious about this.

454
00:20:29,416 --> 00:20:32,583
NEAR: It is serious if they're
both truly in love with him.

455
00:20:32,616 --> 00:20:34,916
They will not easily betray him.

456
00:20:34,949 --> 00:20:37,283
In fact, they'll likely
do whatever he asks.

457
00:20:48,816 --> 00:20:50,749
WOMAN: Please stop.

458
00:20:50,783 --> 00:20:52,883
-Aw, come on now, lady.

459
00:20:52,916 --> 00:20:55,883
